## Rule Severity and Fix Behavior

Customize how rules are enforced:

```json
{
  "linter": {
    "rules": {
      "correctness": {
        "noUnusedVariables": {
          "level": "error",
          "fix": "none"
        }
      },
      "style": {
        "useConst": {
          "level": "warn",
          "fix": "unsafe"
        },
        "useTemplate": {
          "level": "warn",
          "fix": "safe"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**Severity levels:**

- `"error"`: Fails build, exits with code 1
- `"warn"`: Shows warning, doesn't fail build
- `"info"`: Informational only
- `"off"`: Disables the rule

**Fix kinds:**

